CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.16
------------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o Full support for API V2, user-friendly call from R
    o CWL Draft 2+ generator in R, create JSON/YAML tool directly
    o 5 Vignettes added for comprehensive tutorials and reference
    o Three examples inlcuded under inst/docker for cwl app examples
    o Auth configuration file to maintain multiple platforms and user account
    o Works for multiple Seven Bridges supported platforms
    o More features like task hook function to ease the automation

    
CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    o Initial version
    o All the APIs of the SBG platform are supported
    o First vignette added
